---
title: ARLE CUDA Scheduler 单步循环 (scheduler/cuda/runtime/scheduler_loop.rs)
---
flowchart TD
  classDef def fill:#e3f2fd,stroke:#1565c0,color:#0d2c4a;
  classDef warn fill:#fff3cd,stroke:#b8860b,color:#5a3e00;
  classDef muted fill:#f5f5f5,stroke:#9e9e9e,color:#555;

  TICK([Tick start]):::def
  ADM["admission.rs<br/>取请求 + 切 chunk<br/>policy.rs / budget.rs"]:::def
  FETCH["fetch.rs<br/>prefix_cache lookup<br/>KV-tier promote"]:::def
  EXEC{"execution.rs<br/>批形态分流"}:::def
  PREFILL["prefill.rs<br/>chunked prefill"]:::def
  DECODE["decode.rs<br/>decode-priority batched"]:::def
  EMIT["core/emit_worker.rs<br/>push token to stream"]:::def
  SLOTS["core/session_slots.rs<br/>slot 生命周期"]:::def

  PREEMPT["preempt + evict<br/>压力回退"]:::warn
  SPEC["scheduler/cuda/spec_path.rs<br/>Phase 2 暂停"]:::warn

  TICK --> ADM
  ADM --> FETCH
  FETCH --> EXEC
  EXEC --> PREFILL
  EXEC --> DECODE
  PREFILL --> EMIT
  DECODE --> EMIT
  EMIT --> SLOTS
  SLOTS -->|loop back| ADM

  PREFILL -.->|压力| PREEMPT
  DECODE -.->|压力| PREEMPT
  PREEMPT -.->|回到 queue| ADM

  DECODE -.->|fork ⚠️| SPEC
